1
00:00:02.002 --> 00:00:07.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47182.1.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>DS9 has been temporarily evacuated</i></c.bg_transparent>

2
00:00:07.882 --> 00:00:11.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>due to a violent plasma disruption.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Until the disturbance ends,</i></c.bg_transparent>

3
00:00:11.511 --> 00:00:14.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>we'll be forced to maintain the station</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>with a skeleton crew.</i></c.bg_transparent>

4
00:00:14.889 --> 00:00:17.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are we holding up?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-So far, so good.</c.bg_transparent>

5
00:00:17.434 --> 00:00:20.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll say one thing for the Cardassians,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they built this place to last.</c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:20.228 --> 00:00:21.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in case it doesn't...</c.bg_transparent>

7
00:00:21.896 --> 00:00:25.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Orinoco</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>prepped and ready at Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:25.275 --> 00:00:26.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any word from Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:26.693 --> 00:00:28.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He and Odo checked in about an hour ago.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:28.319 --> 00:00:30.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They sealed off the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the upper and lower pylons</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:30.780 --> 00:00:32.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and were moving on to the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:33.199 --> 00:00:35.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-O'Brien here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:35.493 --> 00:00:38.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your status, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Almost done, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:42.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've sealed all the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on levels 21, 22, and 23.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:43.084 --> 00:00:44.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still have to check the outer bulkheads</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:44.544 --> 00:00:46.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make sure there hasn't been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any crystallization</c.bg_transparent>

17
00:00:46.838 --> 00:00:48.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the plasma discharges.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>It shouldn't take too long.</i></c.bg_transparent>

18
00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:50.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien out.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:00:52.510 --> 00:00:53.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( faint banging )</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:00:55.180 --> 00:00:56.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you hear that?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:00:57.390 --> 00:00:58.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:00:58.308 --> 00:01:00.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have sworn I heard something.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:04.814 --> 00:01:06.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:06.691 --> 00:01:09.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: You're under strict orders from Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stay in the bar.</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:10.070 --> 00:01:13.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not a prisoner, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I volunteered to stay</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:13.531 --> 00:01:15.033 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and help you protect the station.</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:15.158 --> 00:01:18.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only reason you volunteered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is because there wasn't enough room</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:18.328 --> 00:01:22.415 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the evacuation shuttles</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for 600 bars of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:22.665 --> 00:01:24.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which still doesn't explain</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:24.167 --> 00:01:26.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>what you're doing out here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:28.630 --> 00:01:31.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was saying good-bye to my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:31.382 --> 00:01:35.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your brother?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His shuttle left three hours ago.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:01:36.179 --> 00:01:40.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny... it's only been three hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm already lost without him.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:01:41.017 --> 00:01:42.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please!</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:01:42.727 --> 00:01:44.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've been sitting out here</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:01:44.687 --> 00:01:46.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all this time pining for Rom.</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:48.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I know.</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:01:49.651 --> 00:01:52.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He couldn't find a cup of water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you dropped him in a lake,</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:01:52.362 --> 00:01:56.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but even if he is an idiot,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he's still my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:01:57.158 --> 00:02:00.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you'd betray him in a second</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if it suited your interests.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:02:01.830 --> 00:02:03.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean I don't love him.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:02:03.706 --> 00:02:04.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Odo scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:05.208 --> 00:02:09.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Chief, do you have any brothers?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-As a matter of fact, I have two.</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:10.380 --> 00:02:12.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And did you ever have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to say good-bye to them?</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:02:12.841 --> 00:02:16.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sure, when I joined Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And did it bring a tear to your eye?</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:02:18.680 --> 00:02:19.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose so.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:02:19.973 --> 00:02:23.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, try explaining that to him.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:04:35.775 --> 00:04:38.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity is up 37%.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:04:38.152 --> 00:04:40.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there any way of telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how long it'll last?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:04:40.113 --> 00:04:43.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your guess is as good as mine.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Plasma storms are extremely rare.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:04:44.117 --> 00:04:45.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>But look on the bright side.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:04:45.702 --> 00:04:47.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>This gives us a great</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>opportunity to study one.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:04:47.829 --> 00:04:48.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, lucky us.</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:04:48.871 --> 00:04:50.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should see the view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

55
00:04:50.707 --> 00:04:51.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's simply amazing.</c.bg_transparent>

56
00:04:52.041 --> 00:04:55.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I assume the Promenade is secure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, yes, sir. I've struck the sails</c.bg_transparent>

57
00:04:55.336 --> 00:04:56.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and battened the hatches, so to speak.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:04:57.297 --> 00:04:59.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you better take a look at this.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:05:00.633 --> 00:05:02.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping insistently )</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:05:04.012 --> 00:05:07.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm detecting a small vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>headed this way at one quarter impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:05:08.182 --> 00:05:10.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-KIRA: They're hailing us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:05:12.395 --> 00:05:13.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't get a visual.</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:05:14.105 --> 00:05:16.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: ( static )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:05:16.607 --> 00:05:18.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've been caught by the storm.</i></c.bg_transparent>

65
00:05:18.401 --> 00:05:21.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Our engines have been severely damaged.</i></c.bg_transparent>

66
00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:24.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We need emergency assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you read me?</i></c.bg_transparent>

67
00:05:24.782 --> 00:05:27.327 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Repeat, this is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>...</i></c.bg_transparent>

68
00:05:29.037 --> 00:05:30.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've lost it.</c.bg_transparent>

69
00:05:31.456 --> 00:05:33.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we get a transporter lock on the crew?</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:05:34.917 --> 00:05:36.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, there's too much interference.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:05:37.128 --> 00:05:40.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engage the tractor beam.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in to the closest docking bay.</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There might be casualties.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll get down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:05:42.967 --> 00:05:43.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:05:44.802 --> 00:05:47.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>O'Brien here.</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:05:47.472 --> 00:05:50.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief, we've got some storm victims</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coming in to Docking Bay Five</i></c.bg_transparent>

76
00:05:51.059 --> 00:05:52.226 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>who may be in need of assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>

77
00:05:52.894 --> 00:05:54.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to release the emergency seal</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:56.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the airlock before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they can board the station.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:05:56.314 --> 00:05:57.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:06:09.285 --> 00:06:10.119 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand clear.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:06:14.624 --> 00:06:15.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:06:16.834 --> 00:06:18.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right? Is anyone hurt?</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:06:18.669 --> 00:06:19.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Not yet.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:06:20.296 --> 00:06:22.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What the hell do you think you're doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No questions.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:06:23.424 --> 00:06:26.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a nice way to show your gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We just saved your lives out there.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:06:26.385 --> 00:06:29.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see? The ever-helpful Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:06:30.723 --> 00:06:32.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So predictable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Listen, friend</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:06:32.809 --> 00:06:34.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in case you haven't heard</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:06:34.477 --> 00:06:36.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Federation and the Klingon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Empire are allies now.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:06:36.979 --> 00:06:37.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( spits )</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:06:38.397 --> 00:06:39.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Empire is governed</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:06:39.607 --> 00:06:42.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>by doddering fools</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and frightened old women</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:45.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who aren't worthy of the name "Klingon."</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:06:46.531 --> 00:06:48.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The combadge.</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:06:50.660 --> 00:06:55.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-This one must be the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Go on! What are you waiting for?</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:07:02.588 --> 00:07:03.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a Trill.</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:07:07.885 --> 00:07:10.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You! Shifter! Inside.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:07:12.390 --> 00:07:13.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what if I refuse?</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:07:14.851 --> 00:07:18.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, do as he says</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and no one will get hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:19.021 --> 00:07:22.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Now! Or this one dies.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:46.090 --> 00:07:47.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go...</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:07:47.383 --> 00:07:48.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ally.</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:55.391 --> 00:07:56.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, were there any casualties?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:56.976 --> 00:07:59.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends on you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: What's this all about?</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:59.562 --> 00:08:00.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:08:00.521 --> 00:08:02.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, get the Ferengi.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:08:03.316 --> 00:08:05.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Any more questions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't hurt him.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:08:07.028 --> 00:08:08.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The box.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:08:10.364 --> 00:08:15.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it in your stasis chamber.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, or I will destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:08:16.454 --> 00:08:18.039 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be some kind of threat?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:08:18.706 --> 00:08:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've got Odo in there.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:22.251 --> 00:08:25.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see... Well, in that case...</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:40.186 --> 00:08:42.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still not getting a response</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from O'Brien or Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:42.939 --> 00:08:44.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run a level-3 security scan.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:45.274 --> 00:08:46.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Don't bother.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:49.070 --> 00:08:52.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, take your hands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away from the controls.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:54.617 --> 00:08:55.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now!</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:57.328 --> 00:08:58.871 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get to the center of the room.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:09:02.792 --> 00:09:03.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:14.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:31.404 --> 00:09:33.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get with the others. Move!</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:36.367 --> 00:09:38.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your turn, little man.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:44.333 --> 00:09:47.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't forget to disable the backups</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as well as the primary systems.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:52.300 --> 00:09:55.261 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's my fault, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They caught us by surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:56.053 --> 00:09:59.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow, they must have neutralized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the security systems</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:59.265 --> 00:10:01.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How did they manage that?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:10:01.767 --> 00:10:04.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure but I've got</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a pretty good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:10:04.562 --> 00:10:07.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran across Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an airlock a little while ago.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:10:08.649 --> 00:10:12.028 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When this is over Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I are going to have a little talk.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:10:20.911 --> 00:10:22.246 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know him?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:37.219 --> 00:10:38.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:39.639 --> 00:10:42.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's such a pleasure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business with Klingons.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:42.391 --> 00:10:45.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're so, um... punctual.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:46.562 --> 00:10:49.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your ship was rescued</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>according to plan.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:50.149 --> 00:10:52.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um, I've got your merchandise right here</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:53.778 --> 00:10:56.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but I don't see any latinum.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:56.656 --> 00:10:59.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think you're so clever,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you're stupid.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:59.992 --> 00:11:02.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, there's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for name-calling.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:11:03.663 --> 00:11:05.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>these liquid data chains,</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:11:06.374 --> 00:11:08.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure I can line up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dozens of other buyers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:11:08.959 --> 00:11:10.169 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go right ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:11:11.379 --> 00:11:12.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:11:12.338 --> 00:11:14.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've come all this way,</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:11:15.466 --> 00:11:19.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>braved the storm, just to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the deal is off?</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:11:19.762 --> 00:11:21.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stupid Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:11:21.597 --> 00:11:22.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling nervously )</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:11:24.642 --> 00:11:28.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said no one moves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm Commander of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:11:28.187 --> 00:11:31.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What is your business here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You'll have to ask my employer.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:36.362 --> 00:11:42.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm... I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If everyone would just cooperate</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:42.576 --> 00:11:46.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I promise it will all be over soon.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What will be over soon?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:46.622 --> 00:11:49.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: This is an outrage!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I demand to be released at once!</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:49.959 --> 00:11:51.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Enough of your whining!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Who are these people?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:52.002 --> 00:11:53.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do they want from us?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:53.170 --> 00:11:55.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny. I was about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to ask you that question.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:55.881 --> 00:11:57.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-SISKO: I agree.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:57.716 --> 00:11:58.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now tell me what you want here.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:12:02.638 --> 00:12:03.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:12:05.266 --> 00:12:07.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:12:09.186 --> 00:12:13.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She's not going anywhere with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, no. I don't want the girl.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:12:13.524 --> 00:12:19.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I only want what is rightfully mine...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What should have been mine years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:12:23.868 --> 00:12:25.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:12:26.745 --> 00:12:31.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: The symbiont, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's come to steal my symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:12:42.136 --> 00:12:45.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't remove Jadzia's symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, she'll die.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:12:46.682 --> 00:12:48.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He knows that, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:48.809 --> 00:12:49.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm...</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:50.603 --> 00:12:55.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Please, believe me,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:55.316 --> 00:12:59.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I wish I didn't have to do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then don't.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:13:00.821 --> 00:13:02.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have a choice.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:13:03.365 --> 00:13:08.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... spent my whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>trying to qualify for the joining.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:13:08.496 --> 00:13:14.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... studied constantly,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every day, every waking hour.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:13:15.920 --> 00:13:19.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I sacrificed... everything,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:13:19.590 --> 00:13:23.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and then I went before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the symbiosis evaluation board</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:13:23.594 --> 00:13:24.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And...</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:13:26.013 --> 00:13:31.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They reduced my entire life to one word...</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:13:32.228 --> 00:13:34.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unsuitable.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:35.439 --> 00:13:37.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nothing to be ashamed of.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:37.983 --> 00:13:41.403 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither of my parents</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or my sister underwent symbiosis,</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:42.154 --> 00:13:44.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they live happy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and productive lives.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:44.740 --> 00:13:47.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only one Trill in ten</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is chosen to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:48.160 --> 00:13:50.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's easy for you to say.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They chose you.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:13:51.163 --> 00:13:52.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was one of the lucky ones.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:13:53.207 --> 00:13:54.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now it's Verad's time to be lucky.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:55.626 --> 00:13:56.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Why Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:57.378 --> 00:14:00.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are thousands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of symbionts on Trill. Why her?</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:14:00.631 --> 00:14:02.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did research. I worked it all out.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:14:02.925 --> 00:14:05.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Dax symbiont is the best match for me.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:14:06.053 --> 00:14:09.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have mutual interests,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>science, diplomacy--</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:14:09.181 --> 00:14:12.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad, there is another reason,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>isn't there?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:14:13.519 --> 00:14:14.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:14:15.896 --> 00:14:17.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>After you've stolen the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:14:17.439 --> 00:14:19.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you plan on escaping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant, don't you?</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:14:19.942 --> 00:14:22.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you think of a better place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to start a new life?</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:14:22.528 --> 00:14:26.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand your frustration</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but there could be dozens of reasons</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:14:26.490 --> 00:14:28.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>why the board</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>didn't select you for symbiosis.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:14:29.243 --> 00:14:30.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have to be very careful.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:14:31.745 --> 00:14:35.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An improper joining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can cause permanent psychological damage</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:14:35.958 --> 00:14:38.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to both the symbiont and the host.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:14:39.461 --> 00:14:41.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were only looking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after your best interests.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:14:42.006 --> 00:14:44.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your best interests maybe, but not mine.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:44.967 --> 00:14:50.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All they've done is condemn me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to a life of... of...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:52.683 --> 00:14:53.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mediocrity.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:53.767 --> 00:14:55.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I refuse to accept that.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:55.644 --> 00:14:59.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--I'm not going to spend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the rest of my life dreaming</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:59.648 --> 00:15:03.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>about what I could have been.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:15:04.862 --> 00:15:10.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I should have been.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve... more...</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:15:11.535 --> 00:15:16.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and I'm going to get it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeto, T'Kar, it's time.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:15:18.918 --> 00:15:20.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have no part in this.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:15:22.087 --> 00:15:23.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:15:24.715 --> 00:15:25.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:15:29.178 --> 00:15:30.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:15:30.220 --> 00:15:32.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: Keep away from him, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:15:35.768 --> 00:15:38.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There, you see? I've taken the first step.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:15:41.273 --> 00:15:43.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if I don't get what I want,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my life is over,</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:15:43.943 --> 00:15:48.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so either you help me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or you and your friends will die.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:15:48.530 --> 00:15:49.698 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your choice.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:15:51.492 --> 00:15:52.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll help.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:15:53.661 --> 00:15:55.996 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want anyone else hurt</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because of me.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:15:57.581 --> 00:16:01.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you have to give me your word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one else on this station</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:16:01.460 --> 00:16:02.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:16:02.711 --> 00:16:04.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I promise.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:16:05.547 --> 00:16:06.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:16:09.510 --> 00:16:11.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Julian, please.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:16:22.064 --> 00:16:24.274 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me treat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien's phaser wound first.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:16:24.608 --> 00:16:25.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: It won't take long.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:16:26.318 --> 00:16:28.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an emergency</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>medical kit in the console.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:16:30.823 --> 00:16:31.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get it!</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:16:38.038 --> 00:16:38.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold still, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:16:42.251 --> 00:16:43.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:16:49.174 --> 00:16:50.092 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:16:50.175 --> 00:16:52.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There should be no permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:16:55.097 --> 00:16:58.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apply this every 20 minutes or so.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It should help the wound regenerate.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:16:58.976 --> 00:17:00.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough stalling!</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:17:00.894 --> 00:17:03.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This is no time to be a hero.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:17:04.523 --> 00:17:05.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:17:07.818 --> 00:17:10.195 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't over, Dax. I promise you.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:17:10.487 --> 00:17:11.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:17:14.491 --> 00:17:15.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I know, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:17:16.702 --> 00:17:19.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll do everything you can.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And just in case it isn't enough,</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:17:21.290 --> 00:17:22.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to know it's been fun.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:17:25.544 --> 00:17:26.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Let's go.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:17:33.677 --> 00:17:34.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:17:34.928 --> 00:17:41.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't be long now, and then you'll see.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Everything will be just as I promised.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:17:43.145 --> 00:17:44.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:17:59.703 --> 00:18:01.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: It's a delta wave inducer</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:18:01.914 --> 00:18:03.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to keep you asleep during the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:18:04.124 --> 00:18:06.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It also increases</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your body's natural endorphin production</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:18:06.627 --> 00:18:09.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-to help accelerate the healing process.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want it.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:18:09.421 --> 00:18:11.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I strongly recommend that you use it.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:18:11.215 --> 00:18:13.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The surgery</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be much easier on you if--</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:18:13.467 --> 00:18:15.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your advice.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:18:17.513 --> 00:18:18.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to be awake.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:18:19.515 --> 00:18:23.685 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Use a neuroelectrical suppresser</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and set up a monitor</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:18:23.769 --> 00:18:25.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>so that I can watch the procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:18:26.146 --> 00:18:28.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That way, if you run into any trouble</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can assist you.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:18:30.400 --> 00:18:32.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, let's get started.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:18:41.078 --> 00:18:42.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:49.336 --> 00:18:54.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't blame yourself, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You did everything you could.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:54.341 --> 00:18:55.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I...</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:18:58.679 --> 00:19:00.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will help you sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:19:01.390 --> 00:19:02.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:19:11.692 --> 00:19:12.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:19:20.909 --> 00:19:22.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long can Dax survive</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without the symbiont?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:19:23.328 --> 00:19:26.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once the symbiont is removed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the host usually dies within hours</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:19:28.083 --> 00:19:31.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia is young and healthy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir will do what he can.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:19:33.755 --> 00:19:37.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She'll make it through the night.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That still doesn't give us much time.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:19:37.634 --> 00:19:38.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No talking!</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:19:38.677 --> 00:19:39.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No!</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:53.233 --> 00:19:54.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:54.943 --> 00:19:56.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:59.114 --> 00:20:00.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:20:02.159 --> 00:20:04.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to kill you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, but I will!</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:21:44.678 --> 00:21:45.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:21:46.722 --> 00:21:48.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're going to kill us?</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:21:50.142 --> 00:21:52.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you people sitting around for?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Do something.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:21:52.477 --> 00:21:54.021 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:21:55.105 --> 00:21:58.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the military mastermind.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:21:58.942 --> 00:22:00.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm just a victim of circumstances.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Victim? Really?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:22:01.903 --> 00:22:04.531 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then maybe you'd like to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how four armed terrorists</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:22:04.614 --> 00:22:06.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>got by our docking ring security grid.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:22:06.658 --> 00:22:08.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Security grid?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know anything about...</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:22:08.201 --> 00:22:11.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Save it, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You crossed the line this time.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:22:13.123 --> 00:22:16.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sold us out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now Dax may die because of it.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:22:16.335 --> 00:22:19.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, whatever happens next,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one thing is certain you are through here.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:22:19.546 --> 00:22:21.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarls )</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:22:32.100 --> 00:22:34.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll live.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:22:34.895 --> 00:22:37.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to have to hurt anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:22:37.564 --> 00:22:39.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that to Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:22:40.358 --> 00:22:41.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's different.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:22:43.737 --> 00:22:44.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:22:45.447 --> 00:22:47.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You heard Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't leave him any other choice.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:22:47.908 --> 00:22:51.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No, that's his reason. What's yours?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I owe him.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:22:53.246 --> 00:22:55.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I grew up on the streets of Khefka IV.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:22:55.123 --> 00:22:57.084 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never would have made it out of there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:22:57.542 --> 00:22:59.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was he doing on Khefka IV?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:23:00.337 --> 00:23:03.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the communications clerk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the Federation Consulate.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:23:03.256 --> 00:23:05.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to visit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the accommodation house where I worked.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:23:07.385 --> 00:23:08.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I used to help him relax.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:23:10.680 --> 00:23:13.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When he was recalled to Trill,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he asked me to go with him.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:23:13.517 --> 00:23:16.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We've been together ever since.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And that's it?</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:23:17.687 --> 00:23:21.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He got you out of a bad situation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now you're willing to kill for him?</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:23:22.234 --> 00:23:23.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I owe him my life.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:23:25.070 --> 00:23:27.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can do for him I'll do it.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:23:28.198 --> 00:23:29.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if it means losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:23:32.035 --> 00:23:32.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:23:34.538 --> 00:23:38.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After the surgery Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>won't be just Verad anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:23:39.501 --> 00:23:42.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be a blending of Verad, Dax,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and all the previous hosts,</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:23:43.505 --> 00:23:47.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>their memories, their knowledge,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even their personalities.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:23:48.718 --> 00:23:51.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you'd say things like that.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:23:52.514 --> 00:23:53.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know he'll change.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:23:54.015 --> 00:23:56.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be smarter, more confident,</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:23:56.351 --> 00:23:58.812 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but in all the important ways,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:23:58.895 --> 00:24:01.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if he told you that, he's lying.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:24:02.065 --> 00:24:05.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once a Trill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is joined it's like a rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:24:06.444 --> 00:24:08.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be an entirely different person.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:24:08.613 --> 00:24:10.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to betray Verad, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:24:12.159 --> 00:24:15.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you say. I love him,</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:24:16.663 --> 00:24:19.499 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by him no matter what.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:24:20.458 --> 00:24:21.710 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I never doubted it.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:24:24.754 --> 00:24:25.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:24:29.926 --> 00:24:31.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not just Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:24:32.596 --> 00:24:34.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Verad Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:25:03.627 --> 00:25:04.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take this.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:25:05.295 --> 00:25:08.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on, we haven't got much time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just move it back and forth over the wound</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:25:08.340 --> 00:25:10.175 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in slow, even strokes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why bother?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:25:10.342 --> 00:25:12.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'll be dead in a few hours anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:25:12.594 --> 00:25:14.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if I have anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, help me.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:25:14.721 --> 00:25:15.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:25:16.097 --> 00:25:19.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She let herself be slaughtered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a mindless </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>t'gla.</i></c.bg_transparent>

329
00:25:19.726 --> 00:25:22.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If she wanted to live,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she should have fought back.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:25:22.729 --> 00:25:25.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She did what she did</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save the rest of us.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:25:25.273 --> 00:25:28.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then she is a fool,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and she deserves her fate.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:25:28.818 --> 00:25:30.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now listen to me, Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or whatever your name is.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:25:30.403 --> 00:25:31.488 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't give a damn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about your warrior ethic</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:25:31.571 --> 00:25:32.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or your Klingon philosophy.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:25:32.739 --> 00:25:34.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This woman is dying,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I need your help to save her.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:25:34.699 --> 00:25:36.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, take this instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:25:36.910 --> 00:25:41.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... so the little human</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has some spark after all.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:25:54.094 --> 00:25:56.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping erratically )</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:25:57.222 --> 00:26:00.558 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:26:03.687 --> 00:26:05.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping steadies )</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:26:12.445 --> 00:26:13.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:26:13.989 --> 00:26:18.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, thank God. I thought I'd lost you.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:26:19.119 --> 00:26:20.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:26:23.498 --> 00:26:24.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:26:24.416 --> 00:26:29.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, everything went perfectly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The operation was a complete success.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:26:31.089 --> 00:26:32.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel so alone.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:26:33.758 --> 00:26:35.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got you stabilized.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:26:37.304 --> 00:26:39.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we could get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back in time.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:26:41.308 --> 00:26:42.559 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scared, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:26:44.436 --> 00:26:47.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to die. Do you hear me?</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:26:49.858 --> 00:26:51.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to let you die.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:26:51.526 --> 00:26:56.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shallow breathing )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've never felt so empty.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:26:59.868 --> 00:27:01.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Just rest.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:27:03.663 --> 00:27:04.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:27:06.875 --> 00:27:08.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:27:10.295 --> 00:27:11.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's me.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:27:12.172 --> 00:27:18.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon, Tobin, Jadzia, all the others,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're all a part of you now.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:27:18.303 --> 00:27:22.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's amazing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So many ideas. So many memories.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:27:23.433 --> 00:27:26.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight lifetimes of memories.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It must be incredible.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:27:27.103 --> 00:27:29.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's better than I ever imagined.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:27:29.481 --> 00:27:31.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The station must look very different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to you now.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:27:31.775 --> 00:27:35.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does. I... I know this place.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:27:37.489 --> 00:27:40.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) And I know you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:27:42.285 --> 00:27:44.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course you do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Remember when we first met?</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:27:44.412 --> 00:27:46.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Pelios Station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Anastasia?</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:27:46.456 --> 00:27:48.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that trip we took</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Cliffs of Bole?</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:27:48.792 --> 00:27:50.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both men laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:27:51.544 --> 00:27:53.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: All the months we served</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aboard the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Livingston.</i></c.bg_transparent>

369
00:27:53.713 --> 00:27:56.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And Science Officer Kustanovich.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What was it?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:27:56.466 --> 00:27:58.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight helpings of Andorian Redbat?</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:27:58.718 --> 00:28:00.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:28:02.138 --> 00:28:04.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: I don't think I've ever seen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone eat so much.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:28:05.058 --> 00:28:07.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Remember my wedding?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I remember your bachelor party,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:28:08.019 --> 00:28:09.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or some of it anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:28:11.856 --> 00:28:14.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the time we discovered the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:28:15.610 --> 00:28:16.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My, my, my.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:28:19.531 --> 00:28:21.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of Jadzia's proudest moments.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:28:22.033 --> 00:28:24.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that woman is bleeding to death</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:28:24.869 --> 00:28:28.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'd rather not discuss that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You have to discuss it, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:28:29.541 --> 00:28:31.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know as well as I do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can't let her die.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:28:31.626 --> 00:28:34.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's not going to die.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She'll live on in me.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:28:34.671 --> 00:28:36.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's memories will live on,</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:28:37.298 --> 00:28:40.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia herself will die,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you'll have killed her.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:28:40.927 --> 00:28:44.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think I don't know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll never be able to forget it,</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:28:45.974 --> 00:28:49.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I promise you, Benjamin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do all I can to make up for it.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:28:49.269 --> 00:28:51.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant to hide.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:28:51.938 --> 00:28:56.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are entire worlds who can benefit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from my knowledge and experience.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:28:56.651 --> 00:29:00.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I can help them, and I will.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a better idea.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:29:00.655 --> 00:29:03.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Help Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:29:04.492 --> 00:29:08.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Put the symbiont back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:29:09.873 --> 00:29:12.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even if I wanted to.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:29:12.667 --> 00:29:16.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see? It's too late.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The integration is already underway.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:29:16.671 --> 00:29:20.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's still time to stop it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's life can still be saved.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:29:20.341 --> 00:29:22.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't listen to him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's just trying to confuse you.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:29:22.969 --> 00:29:23.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:29:24.637 --> 00:29:27.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, the symbiont is still weak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:29:28.016 --> 00:29:32.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we attempt another joining so soon,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it might not survive.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:29:33.188 --> 00:29:35.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Are you willing to risk that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I am.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:29:37.525 --> 00:29:40.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:29:40.695 --> 00:29:42.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you wasting your time with him?</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:29:42.989 --> 00:29:44.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he's my friend!</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:29:44.991 --> 00:29:46.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, go watch the others.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:29:51.831 --> 00:29:54.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are still friends, aren't we, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:29:55.043 --> 00:29:55.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope so.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:29:57.754 --> 00:29:59.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:29:59.631 --> 00:30:00.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and prove it.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:30:03.134 --> 00:30:04.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:30:08.848 --> 00:30:15.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then you're not the Dax that I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Our friendship is over.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:30:44.092 --> 00:30:46.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Here, drink this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:30:47.262 --> 00:30:50.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senarian egg broth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll keep your strength up.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:30:51.724 --> 00:30:54.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, don't drink it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It makes no difference to me.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:30:54.477 --> 00:30:55.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:30:56.521 --> 00:30:57.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:31:08.283 --> 00:31:10.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He even looks different, doesn't he?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:31:11.327 --> 00:31:14.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The way he stands,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way he moves, talks.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:31:15.164 --> 00:31:18.668 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He's better than he was.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm glad you think so.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:31:19.627 --> 00:31:20.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:31:21.045 --> 00:31:24.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? The way he dismissed you before?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:31:24.299 --> 00:31:27.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Verad never did that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's under a lot of stress.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:31:27.552 --> 00:31:30.805 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Verad was under stress</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute he stepped onto this station,</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:31:31.598 --> 00:31:33.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but he never turned on you, did he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your point, Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:31:34.100 --> 00:31:35.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you know.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:31:35.977 --> 00:31:37.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're trying to turn me against Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:31:37.979 --> 00:31:41.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad no longer exists.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that better than I do.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:31:41.399 --> 00:31:43.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, then.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Verad Dax, but it won't work.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:31:44.777 --> 00:31:47.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Nothing has changed between us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:31:48.406 --> 00:31:49.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:31:51.659 --> 00:31:52.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:31:54.495 --> 00:31:55.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then make me believe it.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:31:56.539 --> 00:31:59.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go in there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:32:00.460 --> 00:32:01.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Talk to him about what?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:32:02.337 --> 00:32:03.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. Whatever you want.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:32:04.088 --> 00:32:07.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure the two of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a lot to say to one another.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:32:10.637 --> 00:32:12.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want to disturb him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why not?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:32:13.306 --> 00:32:14.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I don't want to!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:32:15.308 --> 00:32:17.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, look at him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting in there all alone.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:32:17.769 --> 00:32:19.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He needs you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:32:19.938 --> 00:32:22.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why you're being so reluctant.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:32:22.315 --> 00:32:24.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the perfect time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the two of you to get reacquainted.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:32:24.734 --> 00:32:27.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said that's enough!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:32:29.447 --> 00:32:30.448 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is anything wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:32:30.740 --> 00:32:32.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, everything's fine.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:32:33.451 --> 00:32:34.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:32:36.245 --> 00:32:37.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be careful.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:32:37.956 --> 00:32:39.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't want anything to happen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:32:57.350 --> 00:32:58.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting and groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:33:00.019 --> 00:33:01.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I got him! I got him!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:33:02.939 --> 00:33:04.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( roaring )</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:33:04.899 --> 00:33:05.817 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay back.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:33:06.359 --> 00:33:08.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:33:09.737 --> 00:33:11.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should talk about this, huh?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:33:12.573 --> 00:33:13.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:33:16.661 --> 00:33:17.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My ear.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:33:18.538 --> 00:33:20.206 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:33:23.626 --> 00:33:24.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pathetic.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:33:25.545 --> 00:33:28.214 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel, take him to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:33:28.673 --> 00:33:30.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:33:40.101 --> 00:33:42.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it now?</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:33:43.354 --> 00:33:45.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please... it hurts.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:33:46.107 --> 00:33:47.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right. Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:33:51.237 --> 00:33:53.197 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The damage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>appears to be fairly superficial.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:33:54.407 --> 00:33:55.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:33:56.492 --> 00:34:02.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Ferengi ears are incredibly sensitive.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So I'd better run some further tests.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:34:02.165 --> 00:34:03.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning loudly )</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:34:09.797 --> 00:34:12.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity's dropped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another 20%.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:34:14.469 --> 00:34:16.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this has been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hard for you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:34:16.429 --> 00:34:19.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been hard for both of us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's almost over.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:34:19.515 --> 00:34:20.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Good.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:34:20.725 --> 00:34:22.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm getting tired of waiting here.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:34:25.438 --> 00:34:28.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Better than ever, thanks to you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:34:30.359 --> 00:34:32.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't have done this without you.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:34:32.737 --> 00:34:36.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would have spent the rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of my life a mediocre man</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:34:36.449 --> 00:34:38.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>only dreaming about what might have been.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:34:40.328 --> 00:34:41.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:34:41.954 --> 00:34:43.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You just worry about getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:34:44.040 --> 00:34:46.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons and I will make sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one stops you.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:34:46.375 --> 00:34:50.004 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Remember, I don't want you staying here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any longer than you have to.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:34:50.129 --> 00:34:52.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me an hour,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then head for the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:34:52.423 --> 00:34:53.758 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The runabout's on Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:34:53.841 --> 00:34:56.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The sooner you leave,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the sooner I can follow</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:34:56.636 --> 00:34:58.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the sooner we'll be together.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:35:04.560 --> 00:35:06.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:35:08.397 --> 00:35:10.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just wait for me at the rendezvous point.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:35:28.126 --> 00:35:29.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:35:29.544 --> 00:35:31.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop whining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or I'll put you out of your misery.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:35:32.046 --> 00:35:33.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not his fault.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:35:33.548 --> 00:35:34.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's got a deep contusion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the auricular lobe</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:35:35.049 --> 00:35:36.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and a possible dislocated malleus.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:35:36.717 --> 00:35:39.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a Ferengi, either condition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could be fatal.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:35:40.763 --> 00:35:43.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if you want him to stop,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>give me a hand with this.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:35:43.599 --> 00:35:45.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not your nurse!</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:35:45.434 --> 00:35:49.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, let's not go through that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just hold this against his ear.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:35:49.230 --> 00:35:51.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( high-pitched whining )</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:35:53.776 --> 00:35:55.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screams )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:35:55.111 --> 00:35:56.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not too hard.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:35:59.031 --> 00:36:00.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:36:00.199 --> 00:36:01.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another second.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:36:04.787 --> 00:36:06.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:36:07.081 --> 00:36:08.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:36:11.669 --> 00:36:12.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:36:14.922 --> 00:36:17.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Doctor. I feel better already.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:36:22.096 --> 00:36:23.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How is she?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:36:24.348 --> 00:36:25.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have her stabilized</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:36:25.391 --> 00:36:27.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but there's no telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how much time she has left.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:36:28.352 --> 00:36:30.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back before it's too late.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:36:31.564 --> 00:36:33.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Odo's in here.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:36:34.233 --> 00:36:35.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is?</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:36:35.151 --> 00:36:37.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, and we've got to get him out.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:36:38.237 --> 00:36:40.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you sure?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:36:41.908 --> 00:36:43.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we knew the access code.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:36:46.204 --> 00:36:47.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow me.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:36:53.044 --> 00:36:55.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping softly )</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:37:01.552 --> 00:37:05.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... standard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Delgorian locking mechanism.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:37:05.598 --> 00:37:06.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sophisticated...</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:37:08.434 --> 00:37:10.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but vulnerable if you know its weaknesses.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:37:10.811 --> 00:37:12.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hand me that laser scalpel.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:37:17.693 --> 00:37:18.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-huh.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:37:23.115 --> 00:37:23.950 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:37:24.492 --> 00:37:25.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicking )</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:37:26.077 --> 00:37:27.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:37:28.246 --> 00:37:29.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( lock releases )</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:37:32.166 --> 00:37:33.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a gift.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:37:35.211 --> 00:37:37.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's decreased another 15%.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:37:37.421 --> 00:37:41.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excellent. That should be more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to allow safe passage to the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:37:42.093 --> 00:37:42.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:37:45.346 --> 00:37:47.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:37:47.807 --> 00:37:49.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, report!</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:37:49.183 --> 00:37:51.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The doctor must have overpowered him.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:37:51.852 --> 00:37:54.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The doctor? Impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:37:54.689 --> 00:37:57.566 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He must have freed the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>T'Kar, get me to the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:37:58.693 --> 00:38:00.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better take a hostage just in case.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:38:01.112 --> 00:38:02.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll go with you.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:04.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I'd love your company, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:38:04.282 --> 00:38:07.118 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but somehow, I don't think you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have my best interests at heart.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:38:07.451 --> 00:38:10.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Kira, I hate to inconvenience you--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:38:10.454 --> 00:38:13.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Odo's free there's no way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're getting off this station.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:38:18.212 --> 00:38:19.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:38:20.381 --> 00:38:21.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:38:23.759 --> 00:38:26.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Benjamin, I guess this is good-bye.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:38:26.637 --> 00:38:29.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not many friendships</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last over two lifetimes.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:38:30.933 --> 00:38:32.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could have made it three.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:38:33.185 --> 00:38:35.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be seeing me again, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:38:59.420 --> 00:39:00.463 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So...</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:39:01.922 --> 00:39:03.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's this rendezvous going to be?</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:39:05.509 --> 00:39:09.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't really expect me to tell you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, but I hope you like it there,</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:39:09.847 --> 00:39:13.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you'll be waiting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Verad a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:39:13.225 --> 00:39:16.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How would you know?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You told me yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:39:17.855 --> 00:39:20.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saw the look on your face</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when he asked you to wait for him.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:39:23.903 --> 00:39:26.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plan was, he was supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get there first.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:39:27.740 --> 00:39:30.034 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That he would wait for me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not the other way around.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:39:30.493 --> 00:39:35.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, maybe it was an honest mistake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A slip of the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:39:35.831 --> 00:39:38.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He lied to me.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:39:40.961 --> 00:39:42.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's never lied to me before.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:39:44.632 --> 00:39:45.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not coming.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:39:47.927 --> 00:39:49.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't need me anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:39:50.137 --> 00:39:52.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:39:53.641 --> 00:39:56.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He does need you now, more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:39:59.105 --> 00:40:00.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never give up, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:40:01.607 --> 00:40:06.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you, I'm not going to betray him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not asking you to.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:40:06.195 --> 00:40:09.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to save him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help us save him.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:40:09.573 --> 00:40:11.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All you care about is Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:40:11.450 --> 00:40:14.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, and you care about Verad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and we can save them both.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:40:16.539 --> 00:40:17.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:40:18.958 --> 00:40:21.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax and Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were never meant to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:40:21.585 --> 00:40:24.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to remove the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>while there's still time.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:40:29.301 --> 00:40:30.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you hurt him...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:40:33.264 --> 00:40:34.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:40:40.646 --> 00:40:42.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt it.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:41:06.297 --> 00:41:08.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ship... it's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:41:08.466 --> 00:41:10.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's because I released</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the docking clamps.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:41:29.737 --> 00:41:31.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like that good-bye</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was a little premature.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:41:32.448 --> 00:41:35.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:41:35.743 --> 00:41:37.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you so sure?</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:41:37.828 --> 00:41:40.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Dax you're talking to, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:41:40.831 --> 00:41:44.210 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both know that if you shoot me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even on stun,</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:41:44.293 --> 00:41:46.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you risk killing the symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:41:46.670 --> 00:41:50.424 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I let you go, Jadzia dies.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:41:50.508 --> 00:41:52.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Dax will live.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:41:53.260 --> 00:41:55.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's one girl's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>compared to eight lifetimes</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:41:56.055 --> 00:41:57.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of knowledge and experience?</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:42:00.935 --> 00:42:04.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that, and so do I.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:42:08.734 --> 00:42:10.236 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good-bye, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:42:13.864 --> 00:42:14.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:42:21.705 --> 00:42:23.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't call me Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:42:24.333 --> 00:42:25.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:42:47.064 --> 00:42:48.107 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel strange.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:42:50.359 --> 00:42:51.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So empty.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:42:51.735 --> 00:42:55.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's over now, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont is back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:42:57.825 --> 00:42:58.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So close.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:43:01.412 --> 00:43:02.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:43:04.748 --> 00:43:06.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it, and...</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:43:08.877 --> 00:43:10.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I'm alone.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:43:11.922 --> 00:43:13.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:43:15.009 --> 00:43:15.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm here.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:43:17.803 --> 00:43:19.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll always be here.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:43:21.599 --> 00:43:23.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't remember any of it.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:43:27.688 --> 00:43:28.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The knowledge...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:43:31.066 --> 00:43:32.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The confidence...</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:43:34.903 --> 00:43:35.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all gone.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:43:37.698 --> 00:43:38.532 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:43:45.789 --> 00:43:46.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:43:52.254 --> 00:43:53.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you?</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:43:53.631 --> 00:43:54.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:43:57.760 --> 00:44:02.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember it all, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>everything he thought, everything he did,</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:44:04.516 --> 00:44:05.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's so sad.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:44:11.231 --> 00:44:12.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess...</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:44:14.234 --> 00:44:15.694 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll always be with me.</c.bg_transparent>

